<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="449" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,151,591]" pageId="3" pageNumber="449">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,316,221,244]" pageId="3" pageNumber="449">Redescription.</emphasis>
Fore femur row IC with 11 setae (IC) (
<figureCitation box="[743,851,221,244]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[151,244,1928,1950]" captionTargetBox="[230,1339,638,1888]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[216,1371,628,1917]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. Favintiga gracilipenis Shang &amp; Zhang. A, C. Male dorsal and lateral view; B. female, dorsal view; D. head and thorax, dorsoanterior view; E. face; F–G. pygofer, lateral and dorsal view; H.valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; I–J. aedeagus, lateral and ventralview;K–L. connective, lateraland ventral view; M. apex of connective,caudal view; N. atriumof aedeagus,caudal view; O.pregenital sternite of female, ventralview;P.forefemur and tibia, anteriorview." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1146419/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="449">Figure 1P</figureCitation>
); macrosetal formula of hind femur 2+2+1; style with apical apophysis acute (
<figureCitation box="[409,555,256,279]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[151,244,1928,1950]" captionTargetBox="[230,1339,638,1888]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[216,1371,628,1917]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. Favintiga gracilipenis Shang &amp; Zhang. A, C. Male dorsal and lateral view; B. female, dorsal view; D. head and thorax, dorsoanterior view; E. face; F–G. pygofer, lateral and dorsal view; H.valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; I–J. aedeagus, lateral and ventralview;K–L. connective, lateraland ventral view; M. apex of connective,caudal view; N. atriumof aedeagus,caudal view; O.pregenital sternite of female, ventralview;P.forefemur and tibia, anteriorview." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1146419/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="449">Figure 1K, L</figureCitation>
); connective with process as long as stem (
<figureCitation box="[1026,1172,256,279]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[151,244,1928,1950]" captionTargetBox="[230,1339,638,1888]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[216,1371,628,1917]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. Favintiga gracilipenis Shang &amp; Zhang. A, C. Male dorsal and lateral view; B. female, dorsal view; D. head and thorax, dorsoanterior view; E. face; F–G. pygofer, lateral and dorsal view; H.valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; I–J. aedeagus, lateral and ventralview;K–L. connective, lateraland ventral view; M. apex of connective,caudal view; N. atriumof aedeagus,caudal view; O.pregenital sternite of female, ventralview;P.forefemur and tibia, anteriorview." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1146419/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="449">Figure 1K, L</figureCitation>
); aedeagal shaft straight without basal dorsal bulge (
<figureCitation box="[455,559,290,313]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[151,244,1928,1950]" captionTargetBox="[230,1339,638,1888]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[216,1371,628,1917]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. Favintiga gracilipenis Shang &amp; Zhang. A, C. Male dorsal and lateral view; B. female, dorsal view; D. head and thorax, dorsoanterior view; E. face; F–G. pygofer, lateral and dorsal view; H.valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; I–J. aedeagus, lateral and ventralview;K–L. connective, lateraland ventral view; M. apex of connective,caudal view; N. atriumof aedeagus,caudal view; O.pregenital sternite of female, ventralview;P.forefemur and tibia, anteriorview." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1146419/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="449">
Figure 
<date box="[535,559,290,313]" pageId="3" pageNumber="449">1I</date>
</figureCitation>
); basolateral processes of aedeagus slightly divergent from shaft at base, nearly equal in length to shaft and with tooth on each near middle (
<figureCitation box="[807,911,325,348]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[151,244,1928,1950]" captionTargetBox="[230,1339,638,1888]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[216,1371,628,1917]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. Favintiga gracilipenis Shang &amp; Zhang. A, C. Male dorsal and lateral view; B. female, dorsal view; D. head and thorax, dorsoanterior view; E. face; F–G. pygofer, lateral and dorsal view; H.valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; I–J. aedeagus, lateral and ventralview;K–L. connective, lateraland ventral view; M. apex of connective,caudal view; N. atriumof aedeagus,caudal view; O.pregenital sternite of female, ventralview;P.forefemur and tibia, anteriorview." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1146419/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="449">Figure 1J</figureCitation>
); basal atrium of aedeagus developed with sides parallel, subapically paired processes suddenly acute to apex (
<figureCitation box="[822,936,360,383]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[151,244,1928,1950]" captionTargetBox="[230,1339,638,1888]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[216,1371,628,1917]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. Favintiga gracilipenis Shang &amp; Zhang. A, C. Male dorsal and lateral view; B. female, dorsal view; D. head and thorax, dorsoanterior view; E. face; F–G. pygofer, lateral and dorsal view; H.valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; I–J. aedeagus, lateral and ventralview;K–L. connective, lateraland ventral view; M. apex of connective,caudal view; N. atriumof aedeagus,caudal view; O.pregenital sternite of female, ventralview;P.forefemur and tibia, anteriorview." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1146419/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="449">Figure 1N</figureCitation>
); female pregenital segment with hind margin produced posteriorly and concave in middle (
<figureCitation box="[633,745,394,417]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[151,244,1928,1950]" captionTargetBox="[230,1339,638,1888]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[216,1371,628,1917]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. Favintiga gracilipenis Shang &amp; Zhang. A, C. Male dorsal and lateral view; B. female, dorsal view; D. head and thorax, dorsoanterior view; E. face; F–G. pygofer, lateral and dorsal view; H.valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; I–J. aedeagus, lateral and ventralview;K–L. connective, lateraland ventral view; M. apex of connective,caudal view; N. atriumof aedeagus,caudal view; O.pregenital sternite of female, ventralview;P.forefemur and tibia, anteriorview." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1146419/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="449">Figure 1O</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
